{"format": "tiptap/v1", "updatedAt": "2026-06-22T09:00:41.485Z", "doc": {"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "image", "attrs": {"src": "data:image/svg+xml;base64,", "alt": "Momentum — concept overview"}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "What Momentum Is"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Momentum"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is an optimization technique that accelerates gradient descent by accumulating \"velocity\" from past gradients, enabling faster and more stable convergence. It's like giving your optimizer "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "inertia"}, {"type": "text", "text": "—a smart push that carries it forward toward the minimum."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The name comes from a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "physical analogy"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": imagine a ball rolling down a valley. The ball picks up speed (momentum) as it rolls downhill, building velocity in the direction of steepest descent."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Why Momentum Matters in Generative AI"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "When training deep neural networks, plain SGD often struggles because the "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "loss landscape"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is problematic:"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Loss Landscape Problem"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Effect on SGD"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Momentum Solution"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Non-convex"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (multiple local minima)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Gets stuck in pits"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Rolls past small bumps"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Flat (saddle regions)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Gradients almost zero → never moves"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Accumulated velocity keeps moving"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "High curvature"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (steep/shallow)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Oscillations, slow convergence"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Smooths zig-zag path"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Noisy gradients"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (stochastic)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Erratic updates"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Averages out noise"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Momentum helps your optimizer "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "build speed in the right direction"}, {"type": "text", "text": " and "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "ignore temporary noise"}, {"type": "text", "text": "."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "How Momentum Works"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The Update Formula"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Standard SGD"}, {"type": "text", "text": " updates weights based only on current gradient:"}]}, {"type": "blockMath", "attrs": {"latex": "w = w - \\text{lr} \\times \\text{gradient}"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Momentum"}, {"type": "text", "text": " adds a velocity term that accumulates past gradients:"}]}, {"type": "blockMath", "attrs": {"latex": "v = \\mu \\times v - \\text{lr} \\times \\text{gradient}"}}, {"type": "blockMath", "attrs": {"latex": "w = w + v"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Where:\n- "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "v"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Velocity (direction and amount of change)\n- "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\mu"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Momentum coefficient (typically 0.9)\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "lr"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Learning rate\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "gradient"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Derivative of loss w.r.t. weights"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Step-by-Step Process"}]}, {"type": "orderedList", "attrs": {"start": 1, "type": null}, "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Initialize velocity"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "v = 0"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " (starts like regular gradient descent)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Update velocity"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "v = \\mu \\times v - \\text{lr} \\times \\text{gradient}"}}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Update weights"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "w = w + v"}}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Repeat"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Each step, "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "v"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " becomes "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\mu"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " fraction of itself plus current gradient"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "If the gradient points in the "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "same direction"}, {"type": "text", "text": " for many steps, "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "v"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " grows, accumulating increasing momentum."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The Physics Analogy (Newton's Second Law)"}]}, {"type": "blockMath", "attrs": {"latex": "Momentum connects to physics through **Newton's Second Law**: \\( F = m \\times a \\) [linkedin](https://www.linkedin.com/posts/gourab-nath-5b1626b0_statistics-deeplearning-datascience-activity-7382924759958867969-tGH3)"}}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Physics Concept"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Deep Learning Equivalent"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Push (Force)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Current negative gradient (gravitational pull)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Momentum"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Ball's accumulated motion (velocity)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Friction"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Factor that decays past motion ("}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\beta"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " or "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\mu"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ")"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Position"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Model parameters "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\theta"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " or "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "w"}}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Gradient Descent starts from rest at every step, often lacking directional consistency and zig-zagging. Momentum "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "carries motion forward"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", blending past and present gradients to maintain direction and stability."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "How Momentum Solves SGD Problems"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Problem 1: Zig-Zag Path"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "text"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Loss landscape (cross-section):\n      |       /\\\n      |      /  \\\n      |     /    \\\n      |    /      \\\n      |___/________\\___\n         ↓ zig-zag"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Without momentum"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Path is zig-zag, wasting time moving sideways"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "With momentum"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Exponentially weighted moving average smooths zig-zag, making path straighter"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The momentum optimizer averages out vertical movement, so net movement is mostly horizontal."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Problem 2: Local Minima"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "text"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Loss landscape with local minima:\n      |  /\\\n      | /  \\      /\\\n      |/    \\    /  \\\n      |      \\__/    \\___\n      |  local   global\n      |  min     min"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Without momentum"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Ball stops in local minimum pit"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "With momentum"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Ball has velocity to roll past small bumps and continue to true minimum"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Problem 3: Flat Regions (Saddle Points)"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "text"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Loss landscape (flat region):\n      |  ____________\n      | /            \\\n      |/              \\\n      |                \\____"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Without momentum"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Gradient ≈ 0 → ball stops"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "With momentum"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Accumulated velocity from previous steps keeps ball moving through flat region"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Momentum in PyTorch"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "SGD with Momentum"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "import torch\nimport torch.optim as optim\n\n# Model parameters\nmodel = torch.nn.Linear(10, 1)\n\n# SGD with momentum (typical practice)\noptimizer = optim.SGD(\n    model.parameters(),\n    lr=0.01,\n    momentum=0.9,      # Momentum coefficient μ [web:137]\n    nesterov=False     # Nesterov momentum (optional)\n)\n\n# Training step\ndata = torch.randn(1, 10)\ntarget = torch.randn(1, 1)\n\noutput = model(data)\nloss = torch.nn.MSELoss()(output, target)\n\noptimizer.zero_grad()\nloss.backward()\noptimizer.step()  # Momentum-included update [web:137]"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Nesterov Momentum (NAG)"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "# Nesterov Accelerated Gradient - corrects overshoot\noptimizer = optim.SGD(\n    model.parameters(),\n    lr=0.01,\n    momentum=0.9,\n    nesterov=True  # Nesterov momentum [web:135]\n)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Nesterov momentum corrects the overshooting problem by looking ahead before updating."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Momentum Coefficient (μ) Selection"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Value"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Effect"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Use Case"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "μ = 0"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "No momentum (standard SGD)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Baseline comparison"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "μ = 0.5"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Low momentum"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Initially, when learning unstable"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "μ = 0.9"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Standard momentum"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Most common, good default"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "μ = 0.95"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "High momentum"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "After learning stabilizes"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "μ ≈ 1"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Very high momentum"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Risk of overshooting"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Typical values"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":\n- Start with "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\mu = 0.5"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " initially\n- Increase to "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\mu = 0.9"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " or higher after learning stabilizes"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Challenges and Trade-offs"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Challenge 1: Overshooting"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "text"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Loss landscape with minimum:\n      |  /\\\n      | /  \\\n      |/    \\__\n      |       \\\n      |        min"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Problem"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": If momentum is too high (μ close to 1), optimizer may overshoot the minimum and bounce around it"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Solution"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Use moderate momentum (0.9) or Nesterov momentum"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Challenge 2: Delayed Settling"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Problem"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Old velocity terms decay slowly, so convergence may oscillate slightly before stabilizing"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Solution"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Nesterov Accelerated Gradient (NAG) or Adam correct this overshoot problem"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Momentum vs. Standard SGD"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Aspect"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "SGD"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "SGD + Momentum"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Direction"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Only current gradient"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Past + current gradient"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Path"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Zig-zagged"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Smooth, straighter"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Speed"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Slower convergence"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Faster convergence"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Local minima"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Gets stuck easily"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Rolls past small bumps"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Flat regions"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Stops (gradient ≈ 0)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Keeps moving via velocity"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Noise"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Erratic updates"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Averages out noise "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "https://d2l.ai/chapter_optimization/momentum.html", "target": "_blank", "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "class": "text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400", "title": null}}], "text": "d2l"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Mental Model"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Think of momentum as "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "rolling a heavy ball down a hill"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}, {"type": "orderedList", "attrs": {"start": 1, "type": null}, "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Initial push"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": First gradient step gives ball initial velocity"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Accumulate speed"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Ball picks up momentum as it rolls downhill"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Overshoot"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Ball may roll past minimum due to accumulated velocity"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Friction"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Momentum coefficient (μ) acts like friction, slowing ball over time"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Settle"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": When hill tilts backward, slope pushes against motion, ball settles near bottom"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Stability"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Ball doesn't wobble side to side—it rolls smoothly"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The key insight: Momentum "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "carries motion forward"}, {"type": "text", "text": " instead of starting fresh at every step."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Key Takeaways"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Momentum"}, {"type": "text", "text": " = Accumulates velocity from past gradients for faster, stable convergence"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Update formula"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "v = \\mu v - \\text{lr} \\times \\text{gradient}"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ", "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "w = w + v"}}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Momentum coefficient (μ)"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Typically 0.9 (standard), 0.5 initially, 0.9+ after stabilization"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Physics analogy"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Like ball rolling down valley with inertia"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Solves SGD problems"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Local minima, flat regions, high curvature, noisy gradients"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Zig-zag → straight"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Smooths oscillations, makes path more direct"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Rolls past bumps"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Accumulated velocity helps escape local minima"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Noisy gradients"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Averages out noise (low-pass filter on gradients) "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "https://d2l.ai/chapter_optimization/momentum.html", "target": "_blank", "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "class": "text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400", "title": null}}], "text": "d2l"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "PyTorch"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "optim.SGD(lr=0.01, momentum=0.9)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Nesterov momentum"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Corrects overshoot by looking ahead (NAG)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Overshooting risk"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": μ too high → bounce around minimum"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Delayed settling"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Old velocity decays slowly → slight oscillation before stabilizing"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Base for Adam"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Momentum is one component of Adam optimizer"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Momentum is a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "fundamental improvement"}, {"type": "text", "text": " to gradient descent that helps neural networks build speed in the right direction and ignore temporary noise, leading to faster and more reliable convergence."}]}]}}